text: Oudenaarde is a municipality in the Belgian province of East Flanders. In 2007, 29,702 people lived there.http://statbel.fgov.be/nl/binaries/Pop%20Bevolk%2001012010_v2_f_tcm325-109882.xls It is at 50° 50 North, 03° 36 East. == References == Category:Municipalities of East Flanders
